{"tid":2278723,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【沒有自由行照顧】楊千FA演唱會，即刻滯銷！","createTime":"2020-11-09T10:20:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-09T13:47:58.000Z","uid":193077,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a7352415b59b0cfbe32160fc136005c55b15ba2e","tid":2278723,"uid":193077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T10:20:36.000Z","msg":"楊千嬅將於下月23日在紅館舉行6場演唱會。<br />\n<br />\n門票在11月5日公開發售，至今仍剩大量門票，銷情慘淡！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n記者翻查城市售票網情況，發現至今仍有大量門票剩，除了12月31日山頂位380元售罄，最貴980元仍餘下少量外，<br />\n<br />\n其餘所有場次980元、680元和380元門票均可輕鬆買到四張相連座位門票，<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相比楊千嬅上次2017年演唱會有天淵之別，當時出現炒賣黃牛，演唱會門票首天開售4分鐘即被掃光，當年楊千嬅開足11場刷新埋自己紀錄。"},{"pid":"830d48eb673bad4969f5ddebe3af024c27125b5e","tid":2278723,"uid":193077,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T10:21:50.000Z","msg":"果然又係中国人搞到大家買唔到飛。"},{"pid":"414dc5175ab8bb279f82686105da7ede5a085fda","tid":2278723,"uid":193077,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T10:25:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f92761ccbae821eff6c97f129d168f637834171e","tid":2278723,"uid":193077,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T10:41:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"363ce27c9b4108fff4b2b80a0aef886679cae97c","tid":2278723,"uid":144014,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T13:47:58.000Z","msg":"善心覆樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}